Articles.Content:
This thread is for your biggest, most insane,Whackjob-esque, strutted-to-hell-and-back creations. Post your monstrosities that really don't need that many SRB's but do, because you can! Post your pictures, and your stories!

This is mine, when I first started playing KSP again, I built the most overenginnered massive ridiculous looking rockets, because I had forgotten about asparagus staging, I called this one, the Trident.

I'm sure it palls in comparison to what you guys have though!

Edited December 15, 2013 by Cavenyanson
